a tad too ostentatious?

4
00:00:08,160 --> 00:00:09,840
You may just want to pull that hood up

5
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:11,120
and go rogue.

6
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:13,560
Roll for stealth you pickpocketing bastards,

7
